{"sta":1,"data":{"subTitle":"终端执行mongo出错提示无法连接","content":"<p>打开终端，直接执行mongo 会提示无法连接到127.0.0.1：27017这种情况</p><p></p><p>原因：没有运行mongoDB服务</p><pre>C:\\Program Files\\MongoDB\\Server\\5.0\\bin&gt;mongo\nMongoDB shell version v5.0.2\nconnecting to: mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/?compressors=disabled&amp;gssapiServiceName=mongodb\nError: couldn't connect to server 127.0.0.1:27017, connection attempt failed: SocketException: Error connecting to 127.0.0.1:27017 :: caused by :: ����Ŀ�����������ܾ����޷����ӡ� :\nconnect@src/mongo/shell/mongo.js:372:17\n@(connect):2:6\nexception: connect failed\nexiting with code 1</pre><p>解决办法</p><p>打开终端，执行 mongod --dbpath L:\\program\\MongoDB\\Server\\5.0\\data（dbpath指向的路径是安装mongoDB时，创建的存放数据目录，就是data那个路径，可根据自己创建的路径位置做对应修改）就ok了</p><p>这时，再打开一个终端，执行mongo 本地连接就成功了</p><p><br></p>"}}